00:01:47.700 --> 00:01:49.000
&gt;&gt; Judy: The available books

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:53.030
in the series will be
presented in a list view.

00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:56.560
The focus will be on the
first book in the list.

00:01:56.560 --> 00:02:00.530
Use the arrow up and down
keys to browse the list.

00:02:00.530 --> 00:02:05.070
From this screen you can add titles
from the series to your wish list,

00:02:05.070 --> 00:02:09.130
download them, or access
their details.

00:02:09.130 --> 00:02:14.640
Additionally, you may change
the sort order of the book list.

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:18.290
If you are going to download
or add to your wish list more

00:02:18.290 --> 00:02:24.210 position:56%
than one title in this series, I
recommend you use the advanced view.

00:02:24.210 --> 00:02:30.050
Switch to the advanced view using
the keyboard shortcut control L.

00:02:30.050 --> 00:02:34.580
Then select the titles you wish
to download using the spacebar.

00:02:34.580 --> 00:02:38.340
