00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:37.360
&gt;&gt; Judy: Once your downloads are
complete your books will be stored

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:40.980
on your BARD Express
bookshelf until you are ready

00:03:40.980 --> 00:03:43.510
to transfer them to a cartridge.

00:03:43.510 --> 00:03:48.390
In addition to browsing the
BARD collection by series,

00:03:48.390 --> 00:03:53.190
you may also use BARD Express to
browse the collection by subject

00:03:53.190 --> 00:03:57.220
by selecting Browse by
Subject from the main menu

00:03:57.220 --> 00:03:58.920
or browse the magazine collection

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:03.650
by selecting browse
magazines from the main menu.

